Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:08.65,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Fukahori Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:03.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,2nd year, class six, seat number 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So she's a year ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:09.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She moved here from Tokyo during \Nher first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Her hobbies are oil painting \Nand fencing with naginata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:13.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Her birthday is February 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's all. Just for your information...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.70,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talkin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.12,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This has gotten as hard as a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:27.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about her, \Nyou get a lump in your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:29.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,so you can't get the food down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely lovesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:37.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,L-Love?! This is what love is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:41.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've never \Nfallen in love before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:42.28,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:49.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. If he really falls for that girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:53.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,then he won't get between Ri-chan and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:59.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we'll skip jazz after school today \Nand meet up to formulate a plan, instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.20,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mikanomachi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.20,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,End of Summer Sale
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hah? At my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:07.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't goin' to Ri'ko's basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to relax more at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.25,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:17.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If we went to that basement, it's possible \NRi-chan would overhear us talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.76,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ri-chan's shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:25.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We live in a row house, so Ri'ko's \Nplace is connected to ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.27,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.92,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Bro! You're \Nback early today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.26,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.30,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, hold on. Where's Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.57,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, Bro's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doin'? Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, this is Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:52.04,Main Dialog,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.38,Main Dialog,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you always \Nlooking out for Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You're too kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy. Dig in, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't have an appetite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can {\i1}always{\i0} eat watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.98,Main Dialog,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro loves his watermelon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.59,Main Dialog,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he wasn't feeling \Nhungry, which is unusual for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:19.49,Main Dialog,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,but I had a hunch he'd be able to \Neat watermelon, so I iced one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:21.41,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.71,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.78,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,We found a weird bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.70,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.77,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.70,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:32.23,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, if you plant a watermelon \Nseed, will it grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.76,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's plant one an' see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.02,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.66,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh, don't cry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A group date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:48.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The four of us will go, \Nincluding Ri-chan and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you started with just the \Ntwo of you, she'd be on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you'll be the \None to invite Miss Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point if you're \Nnot the one who does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.83,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I just don't have it in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:06.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:10.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,My girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:16.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a bad mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:21.14,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, ain't she? Her full \Nname is Sarah Vaughan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,A pigeon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:26.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're really agitated today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:31.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since you keep talking about another girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suddenly enjoying myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.00,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That was so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.07,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.45,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot! Who goes up to the \Ngirl and then runs away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:03.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:04.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the note!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.13,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.64,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...for suddenly interrupting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:27.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to take this \Nopportunity to cult... cult...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.57,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,"Cultivate".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...cultivate... our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,She agreed! She says she'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.01,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to Rendezvous Rock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.92,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I pack us a lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:49.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that'd be great. Just something \Nlight, like onigiri, would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.70,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:55.18,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, just so I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:59.69,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Which of the two of you is inviting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:06.07,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This guy! He insisted on inviting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:10.67,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.36,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.37,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You said okay to a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.47,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It was going as smooth as \Ncan be and then you blew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:26.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I dunno why I said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.80,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wind back time for me, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,As if I can?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,There's Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:42.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just another one of Sentaro's fights...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:46.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:51.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Ri-chan. Actually, one \Nmore person is joining us today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.24,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.54,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.44,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Making lunch took longer \Nthan I thought it would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:03.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're the girl those hooligans \Nwere propositioning at the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You remember her, huh? Actually, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:13.65,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the glasses invited me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Are you alright?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san invited you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:16.85,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What the heck are you doing?! Hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.43,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for a newcomer \Nlike me to intrude...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Get up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:24.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, of course... The more the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:24.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's wrong with you today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.19,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it was Kaoru-san that asked her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.62,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san must have a \Nweakness for pretty faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.41,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:47.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I was just thinking \Nthat your hat is really stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.71,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:51.93,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wore it, I would \Nstill look like a yokel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.18,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.65,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:04.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, when did you change your hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:07.79,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san did it for me. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It looks super. Really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:21.20,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I'm told your family \Nowns a record shop, Ritsuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:25.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Do you like jazz, Yurika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:31.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These two practice playing jazz \Nmusic together just about every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.69,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,They play jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:37.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Kaoru-san plays piano \Nand Sentaro is on drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:41.49,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,That's really something! I know \Nsome people who listen to jazz,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.35,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,but this is my first time meeting \Nanyone who actually plays it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.99,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,My two big brothers like jazz, \Nso I listen too, once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:50.85,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,My brothers frown and get a wrinkle \Nbetween the eyebrows while they listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.41,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,but I prefer music that really \Nhits you with a bang, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.24,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear you play the drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:04.75,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You can't! I still, uh... stink at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:09.12,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you know you can't get better \Nat music unless you have an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.36,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let me hear you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:14.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This... is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.11,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.82,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I think I got scratched by a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:29.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you know? \NLooks like he's got moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:35.78,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I heard a rumor that \Ncouples who climb together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.91,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,to the top of that rock will get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:41.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,No girl's gonna get up that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, you up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.30,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not letting you \Nget away with saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.29,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I can climb that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.48,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Would anyone like to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:04.14,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the sign says it's off \Nlimits... and it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:09.00,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad. I really wanted \Nto see the view from up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.13,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have wolfed it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:23.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Those two seem to be getting on well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:28.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san... You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to pick some flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, this onigiri is huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,In the cruelest of ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:16.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...I made the girl who's \Nmost important to me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:20.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Those shoulders look so \Nsad, but I have no right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.79,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...to try and comfort her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:36.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:38.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.09,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:41.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come with me a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.18,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This! This handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:49.78,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san gave it to me as an \Napology for my towel yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It smells kind of nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't let you pick up this handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear seeing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here about the handkerchief, \Nyou can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:29.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin' about?! Spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:33.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're satisfied as long as you \Nhave this handkerchief, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Go home and sniff on it all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You lookin' to start a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, let go of Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.88,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get rough with him! You \Nowe Kaoru-san an apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:55.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't owe that guy nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.53,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This handkerchief is \Nimportant to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:15.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:20.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Sentaro is drumming away \Nlike a madman right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.59,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, you stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:24.17,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,...and like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:28.24,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to make up if you do it early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:30.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.30,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:36.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, before you moved here, \NSentaro always practiced alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:41.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Shutting himself up in the basement, \Nnot letting anyone near him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even I didn't feel welcome in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:48.68,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since you came, Kaoru-san, \Nthat feeling's been gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.93,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive he was happy to find \Na friend he could play jazz with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:58.96,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, shall I guess what you \Ntwo were fighting about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:03.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You like Yurika-san, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:07.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So you got mad at Sentaro for \Nshowing off that handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,She is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:15.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd been born looking like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:18.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, you're plenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:22.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...a-attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:29.41,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for trying to cheer me up, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:32.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to cheer you up. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.04,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:44.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ri-chan! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:47.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let me out, Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.85,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's the ruckus, Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:55.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't come here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:03.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:14.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He has the same feelings \Nfor the girl he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.17,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't joinin' in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's following along again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's jazz with a festival dance beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! I can't play if I'm laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:37.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, maybe I'll play \Nsomething just for Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:43.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And then... maybe I'll try \Nletting her know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.12,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.08,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.48,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't be so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:05.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...hell is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:16.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Ri-chan is thinking about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:21.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's a song that I'd like to play for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I wanted to practice \Nthe song a little more first...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:39.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but I feel like I have to \Nplay it for her right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,this piece I've secretly been \Npracticing my heart out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:45.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Play through me, Bill Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,"Someday My Prince Will Come".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the title of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:19.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So are you the prince, Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:22.04,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.98,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You've been practicing for Yurika-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And this is your "dress rehearsal"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to give \Nme an answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:51.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to let you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...that there's somebody \Nhere who's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan's eyes are on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:06.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She's always thinking of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that doesn't bother me right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:16.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me that it was possible \Nto fall in love like this.
